sequenceDiagram
    participant AL as Agent Run
    participant H as Hooks[]
    participant LLM as llm.Client
    participant T as Tools[]

    AL->>H: 1. BeforeAgent(state)
    Note over AL,T: Steps 2-5 repeat up to 25 iterations
    AL->>H: 2. ModifyRequest(prompt, msgs)
    H-->>AL: modified prompt, msgs
    AL->>H: 3. WrapModelCall(msgs, next)
    H->>LLM: Call / Stream(request)
    LLM-->>H: Response + tool_calls
    H-->>AL: Response
    AL->>H: 4. AfterModel(state, toolCalls)
    H-->>AL: short-circuit results
    AL->>H: 5. WrapToolCall(call, next)
    H->>T: Execute(args)
    T-->>H: result string
    H-->>AL: ToolResult
    Note over AL: Append results, go to step 2
